General Info
 - PasswdManager a command-line interactive ruby script to create & manage password.
 - The script has been tested with Ruby1.9 and 2.0, with older version cannot be guaranteed runnable.
 - I just insert encrypted password infomation (cypertext) at the end of the script, so we can save the trouble of managing two closely coupled files everywhere.
 

 
Screenshots:

