= Help ===============================================================

> ?
? Print this
pull	Request from remote server
push	Push new password to remote server
q	Quit
um	Update main password
n	Create new entry
d	Delete a entry
u	Update password
c	Copy to clipboard
s	Show passwd on terminal

    name                 uername              last modified time
[0] github               username             2013-08-16 16:21:58 +0800
[1] gmail                username             2013-08-16 16:22:05 +0800
> 

======================================================================



= Create a entry =====================================================

    name                 uername              last modified time
[0] github               username             2013-08-16 16:21:58 +0800
> n

Create a new entry
Entry name > gmail
Username > username
Password > 
Passwd length (default 15) 
Password combination (default 7): 
  4 - digit - [0-9]
  2 - charactar [a-zA-Z]
  1 - special charactor [p]
> 

    name                 uername              last modified time
[0] github               username             2013-08-16 16:21:58 +0800
[1] gmail                username             2013-08-16 16:25:57 +0800
> 

======================================================================



= Copy password of 'github' to clipboard==============================

    name                 uername              last modified time
[0] github               username             2013-08-16 16:21:58 +0800
[1] gmail                username             2013-08-16 16:25:57 +0800
> c 0
# Press Any key to clear password from clipbord #

